ay</span><hr size=1> Well, today I travelled to Rathe Mountains!<br>
I entered and while waiting for my guild, I decided that I would go and help out some of the poor HG's, mercilessly being killed for their money, so I figured I would hold their money while they fought, give them a better chance, and if they died, well, it was my &quot;inheritence&quot; for being so thoughtful.<br>
<br>
Well, *hides his eyes in shame* on my first giant, for the first time, in the past 7 levels! (been caught before, just not recently)  I was caught by the two killing these poor giants.  Well, had they just asked me to quit helping the giants, I would have obliged and moved on to the next dynamic duo, or uno.  But no, they decided to spam me in /rude 's, OOC to the zone that a rogue was stealing from their pulls (zone laughed at them and told them I was being roguely anyway).  Well, this made them even more angry, so they both petitioned me.  Unworried I continued cleaning out the giants on top of the hill, and when they were pulled, I would stop of course, but they just wouldn't leave me alone!  When they realized no guide/GM was coming to ban me for using pickpocket, then leaving after caught, they continued their uneeded tirade in OOC.<br>
<br>
So I gave em a nice chewing out in OCC &amp; got several sympathetic tells and listened to the zone side with the rogue.<br>
<br>
Ahhhh...<br>
All in a day's work.<br>
